AverageDailyBalanceReport is a List
    title is "AverageDailyBalance"
    search form is ADBReportViewSearch
        use as filter
    card view is ADBReportCardView
        row separator is horizontal rule
    Display Fields
    Instance Selection
        where (AverageDailyBalance)
    restrict action CurrencyRevaluation
    restrict action FunctionalRevaluation
    restrict action CurrencyTranslation
    restrict action CurrencyLedgerSetup
    restrict action DeleteTransactionData
    restrict action PurgeGainLossTransactionDetail
    restrict action DeleteEntityOrLedgerData
    restrict action ProcessDailyAverage
    restrict action BuildDailyTotalForADB
    restrict action BuildADBByYear
    restrict action CreateSummaryAccountingEntity
    restrict action Create
    restrict action Update
    restrict action Delete
    Detail Sections
        AggregateBalance
            visible when (FinanceEnterpriseGroup.ExistingAverageDailyBalanceProcess)
            list is ADBAggregateBalanceRel.ADBAggregateBalanceReport
        AggregatePerPeriod
            title is "AggregateBalance"
            visible when (FinanceEnterpriseGroup.ConsolidatedLedgerInADB)
            list is AverageDailyBalanceAggregateRel.ADBAggregateBalanceReport
        AggregateByLedgerPerPeriod
            title is "AggregateBalance"
            visible when (FinanceEnterpriseGroup.IncludeLedgerInAverageDailyBalance)
            list is ByBasisLedgerADBAggregateRel.ADBAggregateBalanceReport
